Package: InflammationIndex
Type: Package
Title: R Package for Creating an Inflammation Index to Analyse Microglia Morphology
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Devin Clarke
Maintainer: Devin Clarke <devinclarke440@gmail.com>
Description: Reads in data produced by the ImageJ 'Microglia Morphology Analysis' plugin before using it to construct a single metric sensitive to the change present in changing data. This can then be applied to novel data. More information is in the associated publication and README files.
License: GPL 3
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Depends:
  data.table,
  nlme,
  ROCR,
  stringr,
  tidyr